data.description: Great location! Open concept split floor plan with luxurious laminate flooring throughout. This home features 4 bedrooms (two Primary bedrooms) and 3 bathrooms. Further features include Samsung appliances (Gas Stove), shaker cabinets with granite counter-tops, and indoor laundry room. New HVAC. LED dimmer-controlled recessed lighting in living/dining area. Over-sized yard for entertaining, and detached two car garage. Conveniently located next to the best ranking schools in Florida, Eglin AFB, Duke Field, 7th SFG, and Hurlburt. NO HOA!
